{"tid":2512555,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"香港有咩設計學校好讀？","createTime":"2021-05-01T20:42:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T12:25:57.000Z","uid":207470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a0c2d8c226575e908ed10c78508e167c5360656b","tid":2512555,"uid":207470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T20:42:42.000Z","msg":"知道喺香港設計俾狗做<br />\n我純粹創作上需要有圖像去support,<br />\n所以想學平面設計，唔係想入行<br />\n<br />\n查咗好耐搵到兩間CO1同香港設計學校似乎最正路<br />\n其他以前出名嘅明愛白英奇、正形似乎收哂皮<br />\n所以喺到想問有無手足喺呢啲學校讀過：<br />\n師資、讀書環境、同學質素等？<br />\n我諗住讀一年左右嘅diploma<br />\n<br />\nThanksssssss<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7cb9de206903784e1819674e0b1aa9d2f060a82","tid":2512555,"uid":28181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T20:53:22.000Z","msg":"軟件上YouTube睇勁過學店d19老師十倍<br />\nPs: <a href=\"https://youtube.com/c/PiXimperfect\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fc%2FPiXimperfect&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNj%2BzTm40CM4Hl%2BPVqeZuRg0%3D&h=3e3ed83a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtube.com/c/PiXimperfect</a><br />\n應該係全世界最勁既ps教學 沒有之一<br />\n<br />\n理論睇大師既書（原研哉 佐騰卓⋯⋯）～<br />\n睇下展 聽下talk 香港其實都幾多（openground/大館/PMQ)<br />\n學店呃錢～"},{"pid":"0722fa6f3320380f998d5c616b8c6fed019e0e82","tid":2512555,"uid":370409,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T20:58:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.mpweekly.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpweekly.com&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNj%2BzTm40CM4Hl%2BPVqeZuRg0%3D&h=d6430182\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpweekly.com</a> &rsaquo; ...<br />\n薩凡納藝術設計學院（SCAD）宣佈結束香港分校-藝文- 明周文化"},{"pid":"1be1b58cb17b2fe2deb33a631a6f03f9cd78e15a","tid":2512555,"uid":16383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T21:54:42.000Z","msg":"唔好介意，巴打 平面設計真係講天份，讀幾多書學幾多理論都係冇用。攞張所謂嘅沙紙都係廢，我敢講讀完都係學唔到嘢。靈感同天份呢方面，真係靠讀書真係學唔嚟。<br />\n建議你報個photoshop+Ai嘅雞精班讀吓 摸吓啲應用程式點用，上YouTube 睇吓片，留意吓所有生活有關嘅平面設計（例如：人地卡片、廣告排版、傳單等等）總之有圖，有排版嘅嘢乜都睇一餐 研究吓人地點解會咁排版 咁整，係可以訓練吓啲靈感，會練到對顏色嘅觸角，同埋了解到時下風格走向。除此之外，真係冇乜外來嘢係幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />設計呢啲嘢有人做咗十幾年，讀咗好多書，整啲嘢都係啲不知所謂嘅長輩圖，有啲人上網自學ps幾個制點撳就做大型廣告版。<br />\n<br />\n利申：我係日日食緊屎嘅設計狗。我就慘啲，要做埋所有前期工作 由拍攝，拍片，到後期設計，排版，剪接，文案一腳踏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccf7b14a812f92535c42235f7962599dec7acb7c","tid":2512555,"uid":16383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T21:59:35.000Z","msg":"同埋既然唔係想入呢行，無需要去讀埋啲咩文憑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過，我都係作為一個過來人嘅睇法啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"256c278138ca4d582b899cc2df12acab1aff46bd","tid":2512555,"uid":330450,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T22:01:57.000Z","msg":"讀乜鳩都唔好讀HKDI<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你老母一失足成千古恨"},{"pid":"28ca3ccd359789ca731de7e9da6e43b50916cbd5","tid":2512555,"uid":339397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"256c278138ca4d582b899cc2df12acab1aff46bd","tid":2512555,"uid":330450,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T22:01:57.000Z","msg":"讀乜鳩都唔好讀HKDI<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你老母一失足成千古恨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T22:08:06.000Z","msg":"How bad?"},{"pid":"e2ee95ed8874749a9b7161b57d712153588d4a16","tid":2512555,"uid":129309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"256c278138ca4d582b899cc2df12acab1aff46bd","tid":2512555,"uid":330450,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T22:01:57.000Z","msg":"讀乜鳩都唔好讀HKDI<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你老母一失足成千古恨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T22:11:38.000Z","msg":"學費係咪可以有vplus平幾成"},{"pid":"13e543ec93068a4f478a97097d143a3f17732f12","tid":2512555,"uid":138707,"lik